"ini\",\"ada\",\"tentu\",\"tentu\",\"yang\",\"sifat\",\"formil\",\"tentang\",\"cara\",\"mohon\",\"izin\",\"minta\",\"banding\",\"hadap\",\"tolak\",\"mohon\",\"izin\",\"dan\",\"terus\",\"samping\",\"itu\",\"perlu\",\"jelas\",\"bahwa\",\"bilamana\",\"jadi\",\"putus\",\"hubung\",\"kerja\",\"cara\",\"besar\",\"besar\",\"bagai\",\"akibat\",\"dari\",\"tindak\",\"perintah\",\"maka\",\"perintah\",\"akan\",\"usaha\",\"untuk\",\"ringan\",\"beban\",\"kaum\",\"buruh\",\"itu\",\"dan\",\"akan\",\"usaha\",\"salur\",\"mereka\",\"pada\",\"perusahaanproyek\",\"yang\",\"lain\",\"demikian\",\"juga\",\"putus\",\"hubung\",\"kerja\",\"karena\",\"akibat\",\"modernisasi\",\"otomatisasi\",\"effisiency\",\"dan\",\"rationalisasi\",\"yang\",\"tuju\",\"oleh\",\"perintah\",\"dapat\",\"perhati\",\"perintah\",\"sepenuh\",\"dengan\",\"jalan\",\"usaha\",\"cara\",\"aktif\",\"salur\",\"buruh\",\"buruh\",\"itu\",\"keperusahaanproyek\",\"lain\",\"pasal\",\"demi\",\"pasal\",\"pasal\",\"cukup\",\"jelas\",\"pasal\",\"cukup\",\"jelas\",\"pasal\",\"sekira\",\"sini\",\"muka\",\"bahwa\",\"jumlah\",\"puluh\",\"maksud\",\"pada\",\"pasal\",\"ayat\",\"hanya\",\"rupa\",\"ancar\",\"ancar\",\"ukur\",\"yang\",\"penting\",\"yalah\",\"maksudhasrat\",\"usaha\",\"untuk\",\"putus\",\"hubung\",\"kerja\",\"cara\",\"besar\",\"besar\",\"pasal\",\"a\",\"name\",\"img\",\"srcuploadspdftohtmlarsiphtml\",\"jpg\",\"presiden\",\"republik\",\"indonesia\",\"pasal\",\"dalam\",\"masa\",\"coba\",\"turut\",\"hukum\",\"yang\",\"laku\",\"dua\",\"pihak\",\"wenang\",\"untuk\",\"putus\",\"hubung\",\"kerja\",\"ketika\",\"asas\",\"sebut\",\"telah\",\"tahan\",\"dalam\",\"undang\",\"undang\",\"ini\",\"pasal\",\"sd\",\"atur\",\"tata\",\"cara\",\"mohon\",\"izin\",\"dan\",\"lain\",\"lain\",\"hal\",\"yang\",\"sifat\",\"formil\",\"sehingga\",\"tidak\",\"perlu\",\"jelas\",\"lebih\",\"lanjut\",\"pasal\",\"cukup\",\"jelas\",\"pasal\",\"cukup\",\"jelas\",\"pasal\",\"dasar\",\"pasal\",\"ini\",\"semua\",\"buruh\",\"masuk\",\"buruh\",\"contractor\",\"dengan\",\"tidak\",\"hirau\",\"apakah\",\"mereka\",\"buruh\",\"hari\",\"bulan\",\"atau\",\"borong\",\"op\",\"stuikloon\",\"lindung\",\"oleh\",\"undang\",\"undang\",\"ini\",\"yang\",\"maksud\",\"dengan\",\"usaha\",\"yalah\",\"usaha\",\"yang\",\"tidak\",\"status\",\"usaha\",\"negara\",\"atau\",\"usaha\",\"daerah\",\"dan\",\"yang\",\"rupa\",\"organisasi\",\"dari\",\"alat\",\"alat\",\"produksi\",\"untuk\",\"hasil\",\"barang\",\"barang\",\"atau\",\"jasa\",\"guna\",\"muas\",\"butuh\",\"masyarakat\",\"adapun\",\"kena\",\"putus\",\"hubung\",\"kerja\",\"usaha\",\"usaha\",\"negara\",\"dan\",\"daerah\",\"perintah\",\"maksud\",\"ada\",\"atur\",\"sendiri\",\"pasal\",\"dan\",\"cukup\",\"jelas\",\"tambah\",\"lembar\",\"negara\",\"nomor\",\"html\"]', 125);
